### 4. **GENERATOR PROCESS - RPC Client**
**Location:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775491965006-gcblk5/packages/generator-helper/src/GeneratorProcess.ts`

